text: Dishonest in their weighing scale. The weighing scale was not in customer range. The Indian man said it weighed 570gm but when I took it home and weighed it, it was only 562 gm. He profited by more than 50¢. If he cheated many customer, he can earn a lot of money. Authority must take action against this  dishonest shop.

author_name: Energy Plus Oils & Organics (எனர்ஜி ப்ளஸ் ஆயில்ஸ்)
